### File Manager API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/file-manager

### 1. Get Complete File Tree (Root)
# Returns hierarchical structure of all files and folders from root
GET http://localhost:8080/file-manager/tree
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get File Tree for Specific Path
# Returns file tree starting from a specific subdirectory
GET http://localhost:8080/file-manager/tree?path=uploads
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Get File Tree for Another Path
GET http://localhost:8080/file-manager/tree?path=documents/2025
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Get All Files (Flat List)
# Returns a flat list of all files without folder structure
GET http://localhost:8080/file-manager/files
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Get Storage Statistics
# Returns total size, file count, and folder count
GET http://localhost:8080/file-manager/stats
Content-Type: application/json

###

